## Domain capabilities (the `datavidence-healthanalysis` plugin — health-data profile)

_Install separately; call explicitly with `/datavidence-healthanalysis:<name>`. The
project still works without it (the step is then done by hand)._

| Capability | Kind | Reliable triggers | When NOT |
|---|---|---|---|
| `phenotype-scaffold` | skill | "define / operationalize a phenotype", "computable case definition" | a static one-code label with no time logic |
| `code-list-validate` | skill | "validate this code list / mapping", "check ICD/SNOMED/RxNorm provenance" | codes are the endpoint, not grouped |
| `indicator-review` | skill | "review this denominator / numerator / window / episode design" | no cohort/indicator construction involved |
